an eighth grade education.

00:29:25.560 --> 00:29:27.860
And now his grandson's
standing here getting paid

00:29:27.860 --> 00:29:29.640
to speak at Harvard University.

00:29:29.640 --> 00:29:31.203
Where are a testament
to that love.

