00:31:40.720 --> 00:31:41.950
So let me in my zone.

00:31:41.950 --> 00:31:43.260
Throw this dog a bone.

00:31:43.260 --> 00:31:46.100
Because I spit bars for
those native kids at home

00:31:46.100 --> 00:31:48.700
