whose dreams go far.

00:31:48.700 --> 00:31:49.890
You've got a jump shot.

00:31:49.890 --> 00:31:51.550
You're a red superstar.

00:31:51.550 --> 00:31:54.210
Take a cruise in the
car, disregard the law.

00:31:54.210 --> 00:31:57.030
We don't know no better
when adults withdraw.

00:31:57.030 --> 00:31:59.770
Bumpin first of the month
on the first of the month,

00:31:59.770 --> 00:32:02.500
from the womb to the hearse,
that ensures what I want.

00:32:02.500 --> 00:32:05.005
Selling food stamps, I
