00:32:15.680 --> 00:32:18.540
We still face genocide
in this colonial state.

00:32:18.540 --> 00:32:19.780
Our ceremonies were banned.

00:32:19.780 --> 00:32:21.170
They cut our grandpa's braids.

00:32:21.170 --> 00:32:24.020
