00:32:29.820 --> 00:32:32.870
There ain't no stopping this
rez life from blinding us.

00:32:32.870 --> 00:32:35.920
Ain't no stopping these
problems from finding us.

00:32:35.920 --> 00:32:40.810
Still I run with nowhere to go,
a rosebud with nowhere to grow.

00:32:40.810 --> 00:32:44.000
In the Wild, Wild West,
y'all, the Wild West.

00:32:44.000 --> 00:32:47.270
Living that rez life,
so stressed in the Wild,

00:32:47.270 --> 00:32:49.510
Wild West, y'all, the Wild West.

00:32:49.510 --> 00:32:51.760
We're living that rez life.

00:32:51.760 --> 00:32:54.489
Birth of a rebel, I revel
