00:32:58.874 --> 00:33:00.040
Y'all can't get on my level.

00:33:00.040 --> 00:33:01.460
Gimme bass, gimme treble.

00:33:01.460 --> 00:33:02.750
I'm trouble but never tremble.

00:33:02.750 --> 00:33:05.840
Rekindle the seven council
fires, keeper of the flame,

00:33:05.840 --> 00:33:07.430
land of the burnt thigh.

00:33:07.430 --> 00:33:08.880
It's even in my name.

00:33:08.880 --> 00:33:10.880
I'm a symbol, Sicangu
is how I rumble.

00:33:10.880 --> 00:33:12.889
I may stumble, but my
people are warriors,

00:33:12.889 --> 00:33:13.805
