00:33:19.440 --> 00:33:22.230
My ancestors ain't die
for me to lie on my back.

00:33:22.230 --> 00:33:23.540
Can't take it sitting down.

00:33:23.540 --> 00:33:25.020
Instead I'm fighting back.

00:33:25.020 --> 00:33:26.880
Buck your system,
buck your capitalism.

00:33:26.880 --> 00:33:29.560
You took the land, made us
sick, and gave us alcoholism.

00:33:29.560 --> 00:33:31.000
You took away our wisdom.

00:33:31.000 --> 00:33:32.330
You took away our health.

00:33:32.330 --> 00:33:35.220
We're going to get it back, and
we're going to honor ourselves.

00:33:35.220 --> 00:33:38.340
In the Wild, Wild West,
y'all, the Wild West.

00:33:38.340 --> 00:33:42.220
Living that rez life, so
blessed in the Wild, Wild West,

00:33:42.220 --> 00:33:43.820
y'all, the Wild West.

00:33:43.820 --> 00:33:46.162
We're living that rez life.

00:33:46.162 --> 00:33:49.290
You forced our culture
underground, underground,

00:33:49.290 --> 00:33:52.300
but you ain't stopping
no one now, no one now.

00:33:52.300 --> 00:33:56.201
We're stronger and we know
it now, we know it now.

