00:58:27.110 --> 00:58:29.298
you get through all
those painful times

00:58:29.298 --> 00:58:30.423
or feeling like an outcast.

00:58:33.670 --> 00:58:34.170
-Yeah.

00:58:34.170 --> 00:58:34.890
