00:59:13.110 --> 00:59:16.480
I am very grateful to
my parents and my family

00:59:16.480 --> 00:59:18.832
for sending me there.

00:59:18.832 --> 00:59:20.290
Because you learn
a lot when you're

00:59:20.290 --> 00:59:23.110
uncomfortable for so long.

00:59:23.110 --> 00:59:25.350
I'm also really
grateful for going

00:59:25.350 --> 00:59:31.380
