01:00:03.350 --> 01:00:06.210
again that I found teachers.

01:00:06.210 --> 01:00:08.610
I found teachers who
were going to teach me

01:00:08.610 --> 01:00:12.390
how to be me in this big world
and who were going to support

01:00:12.390 --> 01:00:16.260
me, and they still do, to be
an indigenous person, a Kanaka

01:00:16.260 --> 01:00:16.970
Maoli.

01:00:16.970 --> 01:00:20.880
Wherever I was, even
if I wasn't on island.

01:00:20.880 --> 01:00:21.410
