01:00:42.100 --> 01:00:46.910
I was just so amazed that
you have undergone this epic

01:00:46.910 --> 01:00:52.100
journey to 562
plus, now, nations.

01:00:52.100 --> 01:00:54.680
And I wanted to ask
how important is it

01:00:54.680 --> 01:00:58.790
for you to physically travel
to each of these places

01:00:58.790 --> 01:00:59.570
to do your work?

01:01:05.220 --> 01:01:08.750
-I think it's really important
that we meet people in spaces

01:01:08.750 --> 01:01:10.980
where they feel comfortable.

01:01:10.980 --> 01:01:14.100
And for me, the reason for
going to people's places

01:01:14.100 --> 01:01:16.890
because I am trying
really hard to practice

01:01:16.890 --> 01:01:19.120
indigenous photography methods.

01:01:19.120 --> 01:01:21.600
Which is, as a
photographer, we don't

01:01:21.600 --> 01:01:25.670
ask how I can advance my own
career with somebody else's

01:01:25.670 --> 01:01:29.400
image, or how I can sell
somebody else's agenda.

01:01:29.400 --> 01:01:33.200
But rather, how can I make
myself useful to the people

01:01:33.200 --> 01:01:35.160
that I'm photographing?

01:01:35.160 --> 01:01:38.220
And when I arrive
in a new place,

01:01:38.220 --> 01:01:40.720
the reason I go to their place
is because it's their place,

01:01:40.720 --> 01:01:41.970
and I get to be the guest.

01:01:41.970 --> 01:01:44.220
And I ask them, How would
you like to be photographed?

01:01:44.220 --> 01:01:45.930
And where would you
like to be photographed?

01:01:45.930 --> 01:01:47.388
Where do you feel
most comfortable?

01:01:47.388 --> 01:01:49.160
What best tells your story?

01:01:49.160 --> 01:01:52.240
Yesterday, we talked about it.

01:01:52.240 --> 01:01:53.965
Where would you have
your portrait made?

01:01:57.290 --> 01:01:58.750
And I think for
our people, that's

01:01:58.750 --> 01:02:01.690
within our indigenous homelands,
our indigenous territories.

01:02:01.690 --> 01:02:06.940
And it's important that I make
myself available in that way.

01:02:06.940 --> 01:02:08.530
Yeah.

01:02:08.530 --> 01:02:11.350
-Thank you.

